Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小心：潜意识镇静药 目的地：坦塔罗斯流放殖民地 接收人：特立斯坦·亚当斯医生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,准备传送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready to beam down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,传送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Energize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,出问题了，先生们？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Having trouble, gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不懂问题出在哪儿，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just don't understand the problem, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你正把货物传往一个流放殖民地，伯克利先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're beaming cargo down to a penal colony, Mr. Berkeley.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们开启了安全力场，长官 - 进取号呼叫坦塔罗斯流放地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Their security force field, sir. - USS Enterprise to Tantalus Colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,康复治疗殖民地收到，请讲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rehab colony, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,请求开放安全力场，以便传送货物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Request opening in your force field for beaming down of cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号，收到，安全屏障现已打开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise, affirmative. Our security cover is now open.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,传送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Energize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有货物要上传么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any incoming cargo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就一件，长官，一些研究材料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just one item, sir. Some research material
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要送往斯德哥尔摩的中央监狱管理局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}bound for the Central Bureau of Penology, Stockholm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,坦塔罗斯货物准备上传\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tantalus cargo ready to beam up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，伯克利先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, Mr. Berkeley.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你得重温一下流放殖民地的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You might refamiliarize yourself with the manual
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.35,0:01:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 操作条例 - 马上重温，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- on penal colony procedures. - Immediately, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你可以先把这个锁起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think you can take the time to lock this up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把它放进保险库\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll get a vault assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,机密材料 严禁打开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: To explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻新的生命与新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢地航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}TLF字幕组荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：土豆爱，Nick，jc\N校对：我不是小狗，kmdangdangli，xjCGI{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,第一季 第九集\N思想之匕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历2715.1\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2715.1.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,与坦塔罗斯五号行星上的流放殖民地交换了货物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Exchanged cargo with penal colony on Tantalus V.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,未登陆便直接离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have departed without going ashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是挺想见一下亚当斯医生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would like to have met Dr. Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,自从采纳他的理论管理流放殖民地以来，你去过那些地方吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you been to a penal colony since they started following his theories?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 牢笼就是牢笼，吉姆 - 老骨头，你跟不上时代了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- A cage is a cage, Jim. - You're behind the times, Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们现在更像休闲殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're more like resort colonies now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有消息，舰长，切换至扬声器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Message, captain. Switching to speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,坦塔罗斯殖民地呼叫进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tantalus Colony to Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一个犯人失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we are unable to locate one of our inmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可能有发生暴力案件的隐患\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is a potentially violent case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,很可能躲在上传给你们的箱子里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Possibly hidden in the box we beamed up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一遍，一个犯人失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Repeat. Unable to locate one of our inmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可能有发生暴力案件的隐患 - 进取号收到，待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- This is a potentially violent case. - Enterprise acknowledging. Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,3级安全警报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security alert three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,安全警报，3级戒备，全体部门启动3级戒备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security alert. Condition three. All sections go to alert condition three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可能有一个入侵者登船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We may have an intruder aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,重复一遍，全体部门启动3级戒备，入侵者已经登船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Repeat. All sections to alert condition three. Intruder aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，你是轮机部门的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, you from Engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥，C区，14层甲板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge, section C, deck 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，C区，14层甲板，发现可疑人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, section C, deck 14, reporting trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个穿轮机员制服的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone in Engineering uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,安全控制部，这里是舰桥，派人过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security control, this is the bridge. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我已控制局面，舰长，14层甲板已关闭，搜索进行中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have them, captain. Closing off deck 14, search in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,安全警报，3级戒备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security alert. Condition three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,身高约6英尺4英寸，男，40岁出头，注意防范\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Approximately 6'4", male, early 40s. Approach with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,此人极度危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This man extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,重复一遍，注意严加防范，舰桥通知完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Repeat, approach with extreme caution. Bridge out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不在甲板区域，舰长，他可能已经溜出去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Negative in the deck area, captain. He may have gotten out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,扩大搜索范围至周边区域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Expanding search to adjoining sections.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 进取号呼叫坦塔罗斯殖民地 - 坦塔罗斯殖民地，我是亚当斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Enterprise to Tantalus Colony. - Tantalus Colony, Adams here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当斯医生？我是寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Adams? This is Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的一个犯人好像登上了星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It appears we may have an inmate of yours aboard the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一个传送员被人打昏，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Transporter crewman found unconscious, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,货物箱开着，是空的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cargo case open and empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那就肯定了，医生，他在星舰上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make that definite, doctor. He's aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,十分抱歉，舰长，是我的疏忽，我再重复一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Terribly sorry, captain. I take all the blame. Let me repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他很狡猾且相当暴力，要小心提防他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's clever as well as extremely violent. Take all possible precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会和你保持联系的，医生，完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll keep you posted, doctor. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,全体部门，安全搜索进行中，报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All sections. Security check in progress. Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人行踪不明，收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Over-changer, affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,确认警报级别，各部门展开安全行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Confirm alert conditions. Section operational ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们地球人四千年来，老是赞美有组织的暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You Earth people glorify organised violence for 40 centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,却用监狱对付个体的施暴行为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but you imprison those who employ it privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如此说来，你们族人知道如何应对暴力咯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And, of course, your people found an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们摒除情绪，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We disposed of emotion, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没有情绪化，就没有暴力倾向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where there's no emotion, there's no motive for violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长在哪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's the captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们中哪一个是舰长？ - 我是寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Which one of you is the captain? - I'm Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,凡·格尔德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...Van Gelder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我请求庇护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,用枪指着我吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At gunpoint?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你先答应我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want your promise first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,保证不会把我送回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your word that you won't take me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,回坦塔罗斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To Tantalus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不答应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:07:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把武器给我 - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Give me the weapon. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不，我不回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. No, I'm not going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我会先让你的飞船瘫痪，想清楚，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll disable your vessel first. You choose, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我会摧毁飞船的控制面板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll destroy your control panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把他带到医务室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take him to Sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,返航\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reverse course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,返回坦塔罗斯殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Head back for Tantalus Colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不正常，意料之中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Abnormal, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是精神分裂症，不是组织损伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not schizophrenia, tissue damage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是我熟悉的任何情况，吉姆，带他到这儿后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or any condition I'm acquainted with, Jim. And after getting him here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,用了3倍剂量的镇静剂才让他稳定下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it took almost a triple dose of sedative to put him under.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,报告称他相当健谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The report said he was quite talkative.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但没什么实质内容\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But not very informative.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,刚说起一件事，好像马上就忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Claim one thing, then he seemed to forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,然后又开始说别的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and then he'd start to claim something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但话里不时透露出一星半点的真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But always with just a ring of truth in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要好好研究一下，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd sure like to study this one, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他不再是我们的麻烦了，老骨头 - 你这个自以为是、乱摁按钮的狗屁军官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Not our problem, Bones. - You smug, button-pushing brass hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,置身事外，那就是你的处事方式吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wash your hands of it. Is that your system?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩都自信满满，是吧？了不起的专业人士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're both quite sure of yourselves, aren't you? Quite expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,把他带回去，让别人操心吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take him back. Let someone else worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你说你的名字叫什么？ - 我的名字？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What did you say your name was? - My name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My name is--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,西蒙…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Simon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,…凡·格尔德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...Van Gelder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是主管…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was the director of--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,主管…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,…坦塔罗斯殖民地的主管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...at the Tantalus Colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,明白我说的了吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我毕业于…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was graduate of--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,于…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我是助理…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was assistant to--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他们已经擦除了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But they've erased it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,擦除了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Erased?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,编辑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Edited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,调整了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Adjusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,颠覆了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Subverted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不会忘记的！我不会忘记的！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I won't forget! I won't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你是那么愚昧无知，你认为我属于那里，对吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're so blind ignorant. You believe I belong back there, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不管死活，噢，我不会让你送我回去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dead or alive. Well, I won't let you take me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不去，我宁愿去死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not going. I'll die first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你听见了吗？我不去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you hear? I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不，不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. No. No
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,估计多久到坦塔罗斯？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Estimating arrival to Tantalus?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,57分钟30秒，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fifty-seven minutes, 30 seconds, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什么让你这么着迷？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's so fascinating?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,船上信息库的一盘身份鉴定磁带\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An identification tape from our ship's library
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,关于西蒙·凡·格尔德医生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on Dr. Simon Van Gelder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 凡·格尔德医生？ - 凡·格尔德医生，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Dr. Van Gelder? - Dr. Van Gelder, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，这是一盘完整的有关他身份证明的磁带\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No mistake. There's a full ID tape on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他在坦塔罗斯殖民地工作多久了？ - 6个月前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Committed to Tantalus Colony when? - Assigned there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他被任命为亚当斯医生的助理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Six months ago, as Dr. Adams' associate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰呼叫地面，坦塔罗斯殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ship to surface. Tantalus Colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 呼叫频道已开通，长官 - 进取号呼叫坦塔罗斯殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Hailing frequency's open, sir. - USs Enterprise to Tantalus Colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,坦塔罗斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tantalus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是寇克舰长，我想和亚当斯医生通话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Captain Kirk. I'd like to speak to Dr. Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等，进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}stand by, Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长，我是亚当斯医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk. Dr. Adams here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当斯医生，关于你们逃脱的犯人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Adams, regarding your escaped man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,凡·格尔德医生还好吧？你的人没受伤吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is Dr. Van Gelder all right? And your people, no injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,无人伤亡，先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No casualties, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这个人是西蒙·凡·格尔德医生吗？ - 是啊，当然是他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- This man is Dr. Simon Van Gelder? - Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定他没事吗？我们一直非常担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're certain he's all right? we've been very concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他处于狂暴状态… - 他并未受到伤害，先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- In the violent state he's in-- - No harm to him, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能通报一下他的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We thought you might enlighten us as to his condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直在做一项实验，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He'd been doing some experimental work, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是一种实验性光束，我们希望用它来改造那些顽固的罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An experimental beam we'd hoped might rehabilitate incorrigibles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,凡·格尔德感到他没有道德上的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Van Gelder felt he hadn't the moral right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,让别人暴露在他没有亲身试验过的光线之下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to expose another man to something he hadn't tried on his own person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真是个悲剧，医生… - 吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Tragedy, doctor-- - Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来不太像真话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That doesn't quite ring true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当斯医生，请稍等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Adams, please stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信亚当斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法解释，但我研究那个病人越多…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't explain it, but the more I study that patient--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不相信他，但你又解释不清\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't believe him, and you can't explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，你可知道，过去的20年里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones, are you aware that in the last 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当斯医生为改革监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Adams has done more to revolutionise,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,改造囚犯，改善囚犯待遇所作出的努力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to humanize prisons and the treatment of prisoners
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,比40个世纪以来，全部其他人所做的都要多吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than all the rest of humanity had done in 40 centuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我去过那些流放殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been to those penal colonies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,自从按照亚当斯的理论管理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}since they've begun following his methods,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 它们不再是牢笼了 - 吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- and they're not cages anymore. - Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,它们成了医治心理疾病的干净、舒适的医院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're clean, decent hospitals for sick minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 吉姆，听我说… - 绅士们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Jim, listen-- - Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议问问亚当斯医生，是否要求凡·格尔德回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I suggest you ask Dr. Adams if he wants Van Gelder returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 亚当斯医生，关于凡·格尔德 - 是的，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Dr. Adams, regarding Van Gelder. - Yes, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以打听一下你们的巡航目的地吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}May I enquire about your patrol destinations?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们路过的地方，有比我们更高级的医疗设备吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you passing near any hospital facilities superior to ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:14:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然希望凡·格尔德得到最好的治疗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like Van Gelder to have the best possible treatment, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，医生，我会和船上的医生沟通一下，稍等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, doctor. I'll take it up with the ship's surgeon. Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，接招吧，你有更好的地方推荐吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, Bones, you've got the ball. You care to recommend a better place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有什么高级设备，他又不是不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are no superior facilities. He knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但问题在于\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that's not the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果下面出了什么不寻常的状况…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If something unusual is going on down there--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你这只是假设，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An assumption, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须在医疗日志上记下所有合理的疑虑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm required to enter any reasonable doubts into my medical log.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那就需要你在你的日志中给出回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That requires you to answer in your log.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当斯医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这相当为难啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is rather embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,根据星舰的规章制度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By strict interpretation of our starship regulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我得介入调查此事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm required to initiate an investigation of this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如此，才能酌情上报… - 不用道歉，寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- so that a proper report-- - No need to apologise, Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上，如果你下来亲自察看一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In fact, I'd take it as a personal favour
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,反倒是在帮我的忙呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if you'd beam down and look into it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定也知道我们这儿的访客其实不多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sure you realise we don't get too many visitors here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，如果你能尽量少带随员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I would appreciate it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我将不甚感激\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if you could come down with a minimum staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,本殖民地必须尽量减少与外界的联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're forced to limit outside contact as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Affirmative, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前去过那些康复治疗殖民地，进取号通话完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've visited rehab colonies before. Enterprise out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可能，给我在你的部门找个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Find me someone in your department with psychiatric
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在精神病学和监狱管理学方面都有经验的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and penology experience, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历2715.2\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2715.2.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,r星舰运行在坦塔罗斯五号行星的同步轨道上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Standard orbit, planet Tantalus V.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,任务：根据船医的医疗日志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mission: Routine investigation and report
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将进行一次例行调查和报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as per ship's surgeon's medical log.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,看来这一次，我终于得见亚当斯医生一面了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As for my last entry, it seems I will get to meet Dr. Adams at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但我宁愿是因别的缘由，而与他会面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}However, I would have preferred other circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,医务室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,报告情况，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Report, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,凡·格尔德仍处于躁狂状态，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Van Gelder is still violently agitated, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那在我调查完毕之前，你是打算把他留在这儿吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you'd prefer to keep him here until I complete my investigation, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该这么做，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believe we should, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对了，舰长，我给你安排了专业顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I'm assigning you technical aid, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有个心理学家在康复治疗领域有一定经验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One of our psychiatrists does have a background in rehabilitative therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,诺埃尔医生正在传送室待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Noel. Standing by in the Transporter Room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，医生，到传送室去，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, doctor. Bridge out. Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 坐标？ - 已经锁定，长官，传送准备就绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Coordinates? - Locked in, sir. Ready to beam down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我是海伦·诺埃尔医生，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Helen Noel, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们见过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在科学实验室的圣诞派对上 - 是的，我记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The Science Lab Christmas party. - Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你姗姗来迟 - 没错，我记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You dropped in. - Yes. Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题吗，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Problem, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，转告麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, you tell McCoy that she had better check out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他最好是给我找对了上佳人选\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as the best assistant I ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 传送 - 传送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Energize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是这边，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In here, I presume, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,或许你可以简短点，叫我海伦，舰长，因为…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps it would be simpler if you called me Helen, captain, since--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,现在可不是在开派对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is another time, another place and another situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,升降机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,正在快速下降\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And going down quite a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,心脏差点的人可受不了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wouldn't recommend it for weak hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你好，寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hello, Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这位是…？ - 海伦·诺埃尔医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- And...? - Dr. Helen Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 见到您本人很荣幸，医生 - 谢谢，谢谢，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- A pleasure to finally meet you, sir. - Thank you. Thank you, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 欢迎来到恶魔岛，医生 - 或许你可以叫我海伦，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Welcome to Devil's Island, doctor. - Perhaps you'll call me Helen, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,医生这，医生那，我们都搞不清是在说谁呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With so many titles around, we're not gonna be sure who's talking to who.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没错，请进 - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I shall indeed. Won't you? - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,按规定我要被搜身缴械，对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believe regulations call for me to check my weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,噢不，对你来说没这必要，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, no, no. That won't be necessary in your case, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只要别拿出来就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just keep it out of sight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们要是没有武器傍身的话，会浑身不自在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you people feel as naked without a weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我们没带医疗包一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as we do without a medikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,来干一杯吧，好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A small toast. Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真是蓬荜生辉啊，坦塔罗斯星今日有贵客来访\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's such a great day for us here on Tantalus when we have visitors,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先不论为何而来 - 医生…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- no matter what the excuse. - Doctor--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,得了，舰长，你上次通话时已经道过谦了，别再提了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, now, captain, you made your apology from upstairs. Now forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,信号被力场屏蔽了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't think you'll be able to get through the security screen, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,请稍等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了，现在试试吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here, now try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 寇克呼叫进取号 - 这里是进取号，我是史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk to Enterprise. Come in. - Enterprise. Spock here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,传送坐标设定得非常精确，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your landing coordinates were right on the nose, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已安全到达，现正与亚当斯医生在一起，报告结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We arrived safely, and we're here with Dr. Adams right now. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,收到了，舰长，进取号呼叫结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Affirmative, captain. Enterprise out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哈，莱西，请进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lethe. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,莱西，这是寇克舰长和海伦·诺埃尔医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lethe, this is Captain Kirk and Dr. Helen Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,莱西之前来我们这里接受康复治疗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lethe came to us for rehabilitation and stayed on as a therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在已成为了一名优秀的治疗师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And a very good one too, I might add.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我热爱我的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I love my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以随便问，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go right ahead, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你来这之前…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Before you came here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,与现在截然不同，那时我内心曾充满邪恶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was another person. Malignant, hateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,能告诉我你犯了什么罪吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}May I ask what crime you committed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这有什么关系吗？我已经不再是以前的我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Does it matter? That person no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我们治疗方法的一部分，就是让患者忘掉过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Part of our cure, if you will, captain, is to bury the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如非必要，为什么要让一个人背负沉重的过去…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why should a person go on living with unbearable memories if there's no--?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你也应该有同感吧，医生…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I feel quite sure that you'd concur with me in that, doctor--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,海伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对心理治疗来说，改变记忆模式是必不可少的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A shifting of memory patterns is basic to psychotherapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，现在来干一杯吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes. And now to the toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,请勿介意我们的放纵，莱西，来，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll forgive us, Lethe? There you are, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,敬全人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To all Mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,愿宇宙不再广袤冷漠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}May we never find space so vast,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,愿所有星球不再天寒地冻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}planets so cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,愿不再有空虚的心灵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}heart and mind so empty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,无法感受爱和温暖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that we cannot fill them with love and warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这次参观真是令我印象深刻，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Quite a tour, doctor. Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，卡尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 医生？ - 怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Doctor? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我就怕你会问这个，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was afraid you'd ask about this, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道，人们都不喜欢谈论失败\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One doesn't like to talk about their personal failures, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是一个出了点小差错的实验项目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just an experiment that went wrong, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以看看吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}May I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.59,0:22:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，如果一个项目不成功，也就失去了研究价值…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, if something hasn't worked out and therefore has no scientific value--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能让亚当斯医生来做决定吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shall we leave it up to the doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.76,0:22:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你让我跟来当顾问，舰长…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Since you brought me down here for advice, captain--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，身为舰长，其中一个特权就是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One of the advantages of being a captain, doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然垂询，但不是非得接受建议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is being able to ask for advice without necessarily having to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我看这一轮得判舰长赢，海伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think I'll have to award that round to the captain, Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.15,0:22:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是胳膊拧不过大腿，好吧，那就看看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're fighting over your weight. All right, let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do not require...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,…神经中和器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...neural neutraliser.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,神经中和器？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Neural neutraliser?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你能解释一下吗，凡·格尔德医生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you explain that, Dr. Van Gelder?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一个房间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一个装置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A device.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Door.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,控制面板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Control panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.27,0:22:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,天花板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一个装置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A device.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 光！光！ - 在那个房间里发生了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- A light! Light! - This room, what happens there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,神经中和器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A neural neutraliser.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,尚处于试验阶段，其实我们并不指望能获得多大成果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Experimental. Actually, we don't expect to get much use out of it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,来自上面的光线可以中和脑电波\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That beam from above neutralises brain waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,让病人的心智平和下来，不会对他造成伤害，当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Relaxes the patient's mind. Does him no harm, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.44,0:23:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 效果只是暂时的 - 有个问题，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- and the effects are only temporary. - One question, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.86,0:23:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果它没有优点… - 为什么还要继续使用，对吧，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- If it doesn't do any good-- - Why do we go on using it, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,希望，是的，我们心怀一丝希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hope. Yes. Yes, there's always that slight chance that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,希望它能对一些暴力倾向较严重的患者起作用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it might do some good in the more violent cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.37,0:23:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,镇静剂虽然是好东西，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tranquilizers are fine, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但不断地往人的血管里注入化学药物…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But to continually pump chemicals into a person's bloodstream--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:24:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我想得一样，海伦，我们继续参观吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Exactly my point, Helen. Yes. Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这怎么用？ - 很简单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How does it work? - Quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.47,0:24:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是开关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Off-on switches.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.01,0:24:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这边的旋钮控制着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The large control here changes the strength
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,脑波中和光线的强度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the brain neutralising beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.27,0:24:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我想起过去一位怀疑论者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You remind me of the ancient sceptic who demanded of the wise old sage
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他单脚站立，要求智者把所有的智慧在片刻间倾囊相授\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to be taught all the world's wisdom while standing on one foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.78,0:24:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,人们曾在地球上对这种光线疗法做过试验，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beam neutralising has been experimented with on Earth, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.29,0:24:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我对这种设备并不熟悉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not acquainted with this particular style of equipment,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.37,0:24:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但我可以向你保证，亚当斯医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I can assure you that Dr. Adams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.17,0:24:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是在制造折磨病人的刑具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has not created a chamber of horrors here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.88,0:24:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我并没有说他有这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't mean to suggest that he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.30,0:24:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，我之所以会问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The reason I asked, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.80,0:24:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为你还没有说明凡·格尔德医生是在哪儿受的伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was you haven't mentioned where Dr. Van Gelder's injury occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.18,0:24:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这儿，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right here, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.97,0:24:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.43,0:24:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,格尔德是个很固执的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Simon was a very stubborn man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.10,0:24:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他能长时间暴露在现在这种强度的中和光线下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He could have sat in that room for years with the beam at that volume,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.64,0:25:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至强度更高也没问题，只要他肯让别人陪在旁边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or even higher. Or if he simply had someone standing by
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.73,0:25:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一出现意外就关闭机器，但他并没有这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to snap it off in case he got into trouble. But no.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.90,0:25:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他尝试独自一人做试验，并把强度调到最高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He tried it alone and on full volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.70,0:25:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真是遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.21,0:25:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.72,0:25:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你要忘记你听到的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will forget all you have heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.93,0:25:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你企图回忆，即使是其中的只言片语 你也将感受到可怕的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To remember any portion of it, any word, will cause you pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.52,0:25:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你竭力去回忆，痛苦会更剧烈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Terrible pain, growing more terrible as you fight to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.66,0:25:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,能告诉我你现在在哪儿吗，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you give us your present location, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.12,0:25:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在亚当斯医生的书房，怎么了，史波克先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In Dr. Adams' study, Mr. Spock. why?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.37,0:26:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你现在和亚当斯医生在一起？ - 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Then you're with Dr. Adams now? - Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.04,0:26:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.55,0:26:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,凡·格尔德提到一种治疗设备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Van Gelder has made reference to a particular treatment room.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.39,0:26:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他把它称作神经中和器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The term was "neural neutraliser."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.05,0:26:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，他在那里意外受了伤，我查看过那个房间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, he was injured there. I've seen the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.06,0:26:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当斯医生解释了凡·格尔德的失误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Adams explained the mistake Van Gelder made.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.69,0:26:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，还有别的问题吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go ahead, Mr. Spock. Anything further?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.03,0:26:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你的史波克先生是一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your Mr. Spock sounds like a very excellent
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.57,0:26:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,非常优秀的大副，寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}second in command, Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.57,0:26:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,请让他直言，毋须忌讳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please tell him to go ahead and speak freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.99,0:26:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我现在要去检查工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have to check in with a member of my staff, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.62,0:26:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢，亚当斯医生 - 失陪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Thank you, Dr. Adams. - Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.12,0:26:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand by, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.96,0:26:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当斯医生已经有事离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Adams has left with some things to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.42,0:26:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，史波克先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is it, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.67,0:26:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,凡·格尔德现在极度焦躁不安，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Van Gelder is extremely agitated, captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.51,0:26:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他警告说你现在有危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and warns that you're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.51,0:26:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他在胡说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.10,0:27:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,请再说一遍，舰长，我听不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please repeat, captain. I didn't receive that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.43,0:27:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉麦考伊，他派来的技术顾问认为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell McCoy the technical expert he sent along with me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.85,0:27:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,任何担忧都是多余的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}insists that any concern is unjustified.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.11,0:27:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,根据亚当斯的说法，凡·格尔德是自食其果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}According to Adams, Van Gelder created his own problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.20,0:27:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他的神经突触受到了损伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's suffering from neural synapse damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.61,0:27:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他的大脑现在就像短路了一样，所以才会有幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As if his brain were short-circuited. It's no wonder he's having delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.41,0:27:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是麦考伊，收到，明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McCoy here. Received and understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.83,0:27:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们仍然心存疑虑，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we still have some doubts up here, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.33,0:27:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有别的吩咐吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you tell us any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.67,0:27:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.50,0:27:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算什么时候回来，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when do you plan to beam back up, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.22,0:27:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们会在这过夜，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think we'll spend the night here, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.47,0:27:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不！不要…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No! No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.10,0:27:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,请你每四小时回报一次，没问题吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you will continue to check in every four hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.10,0:27:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.60,0:27:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克呼叫结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.77,0:27:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不！不能让他们在那过夜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No! No, no, don't let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.98,0:27:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要警告你们的舰长，不，不能过夜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must warn your captain. No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.36,0:27:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,别让他留在那，别让他留在那\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't let him stay. Don't let him stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.70,0:28:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不，不要给我打镇静剂，求你了，不要打\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't. No, no, don't hypo me. Please, don't hypo me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.95,0:28:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽量控制住自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll try not to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.83,0:28:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.42,0:28:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们要听好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you must listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.84,0:28:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,警告你们的舰长，亚当斯医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Warn your captain. Dr. Adam--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.84,0:28:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当斯医生…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Adams...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.56,0:28:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 会摧毁… - 摧毁什么？怎么摧毁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- ...will destroy-- - Destroy how? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.69,0:28:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就像死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like death.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.60,0:28:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号日志，我是大副史波克，代理舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise log, First Officer Spock, acting captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.27,0:28:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，我必须使用一种古老的瓦肯技能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must now use an ancient Vulcan technique
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.90,0:29:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,去探索凡·格尔德那饱受折磨的内心世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to probe into Van Gelder's tortured mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.99,0:29:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，只要有一丝希望，就能起点作用的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, if there's the slightest possibility it might help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.82,0:29:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我还从未在人类身上试过这种技术，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have never used it on a human, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.41,0:29:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,无论什么方法，只要能窥探这个人的思想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If there's any way we can look into this man's mind
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.58,0:29:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,搞清楚他说的到底是真是假…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to see if what he's saying is real or delusion--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.62,0:29:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种瓦肯人独有的私秘技能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a hidden, personal thing to the Vulcan people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.00,0:29:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们种族私人生活的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Part of our private lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.21,0:29:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了，史波克，吉姆·寇克可能遇到了大麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, look, Spock, Jim Kirk could be in real trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.67,0:29:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这技能到底灵不灵？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will it work or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.36,0:29:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会有危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It could be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.65,0:29:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.94,0:29:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要改变你的神经内压和血压\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It requires I make pressure changes in your nerves, your blood vessels.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.53,0:29:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须敞开我的心怀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must open my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.24,0:29:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,让我向你发出警告，向你解释清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me warn you, explain to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.63,0:29:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不会影响到你的，麦考伊医生，只有我触碰到的人才会受影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This will not affect you, Dr. McCoy. Only the person I touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.80,0:30:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这可不是催眠 - 我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It is not hypnosis. - I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.45,0:30:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，身体机能读数正变回正常水平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good. The reading's levelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.33,0:30:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你开始感到一种奇妙的幸福感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You begin to feel a strange euphoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.67,0:30:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身体飘起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your body floats.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.68,0:30:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.43,0:30:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始感觉到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I begin to feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.44,0:30:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,敞开你的心怀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Open your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.02,0:31:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起前行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We move together.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.32,0:31:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的心灵相通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our minds sharing the same thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.04,0:31:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 晚上好 - 晚上好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Good evening. - Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.91,0:31:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们下午在这儿看到的囚犯怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What did you think of the inmates we saw here this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.29,0:31:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你本可以等到明天早晨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You could have waited until tomorrow morning
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.21,0:31:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再问我这个问题的 - 我等不及\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- to ask me that, captain. - I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.55,0:31:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们很幸福，改造得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought they were happy, well-adjusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.13,0:31:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但表情有一些木然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But a bit blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.43,0:31:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，如果你是在质疑特里斯坦·亚当斯这种大师的理论…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, if you're questioning the methods of a man like Tristan Adams--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.43,0:31:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我想再去看看那个光线治疗室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like to see that treatment room again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.35,0:31:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过你对光线治疗的理论略知一二？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You say you're somewhat familiar with the theory behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.10,0:31:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对，略知一二\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, somewhat,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.73,0:31:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你只是想表达你对亚当斯医生的怀疑…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but if you'd simply state any doubts you have to Dr. Adams--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.31,0:31:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他撒了谎，他会继续谎话连篇 到头来，我什么都发现不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if he's lying, he'll continue to lie, and I won't find out a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.27,0:31:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一能找出真相的方法，就是亲眼看看那台机器是怎么工作的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The only way I can be sure is to see that machine at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.69,0:31:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我这样做，是不是太不切实际，太不讲究科学了，医生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or is that too impractical and unscientific of me, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.41,0:31:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么样？ - 来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Well? - Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.79,0:32:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们叫什么名字？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is our name?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.88,0:32:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.38,0:32:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是西蒙·凡·格尔德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are Simon Van Gelder.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.60,0:32:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当斯医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Adams,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.68,0:32:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那个神经中和器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the neural neutraliser.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.39,0:32:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他对我们做了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What did he do to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.15,0:32:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他能任意重塑人的心灵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He can reshape any mind he chooses.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.28,0:32:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他用它来抹去我们的记忆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He used it to erase our memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.58,0:32:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把他自己的想法放进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}put his own thoughts there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.04,0:32:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他很惊讶，这机器会消耗那么多的能量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was surprised it took so much power.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.29,0:32:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们反抗了他，还记得吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We fought him, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.34,0:32:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们是那么疲倦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we grew so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.43,0:32:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的心灵是那么空虚，那么无遮无拦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our mind so blank, so open
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.06,0:33:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他放进去的任何思想都变成了我们自己的思想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that any thought he placed there became our thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.06,0:33:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的心灵那么空虚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our mind so empty,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.73,0:33:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,像一块渴求思想的海绵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}like a sponge needing thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.03,0:33:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,乞求着，空虚着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}begging, empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.95,0:33:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,孤独着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.20,0:33:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,空虚地晾在那里，那么孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So lonely to be sitting there empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.63,0:33:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,渴求着他吐出的只言片语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wanting any word from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.84,0:33:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 爱 - 是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Love. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.72,0:33:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 恨 - 是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Hate. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.80,0:33:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 生 - 是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Live. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.93,0:33:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 死 - 是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Die. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.52,0:33:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,空虚得那么煎熬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Such agony, to be empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.61,0:33:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,空虚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.03,0:33:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.61,0:33:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 孤独 - 太空虚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Lonely. - So empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.49,0:34:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,太空虚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.29,0:34:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想让我的大脑受损\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have no desire to damage my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.71,0:34:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这操作起来应该是安全的，是不是？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can this be handled with reasonable safety, yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.75,0:34:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.63,0:34:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你能把握好分寸吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And will you be able to determine
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.17,0:34:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量避免让光线对我造成哪怕最细微的伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if that beam is harming me in the slightest?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.80,0:34:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,能的，舰长，我是内行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, captain. I know my profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.99,0:34:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.49,0:34:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们试试最低强度，一两秒钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll try minimum intensity. A second or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.17,0:34:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好就开始，医生，一两秒就停\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anytime you're ready, doctor. Just for a second or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.38,0:34:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经试过了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We already tried it for that long, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.59,0:34:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也没发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.51,0:34:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有事情发生了，你的表情刚刚一片空白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something happened. Your face went completely blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.55,0:35:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,试个无害的暗示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Try a harmless suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.23,0:35:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你很饿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.61,0:35:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧，等结束了以后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, when we finally get through with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.66,0:35:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我得找个厨房猛吃一顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like to locate and raid a kitchen somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.16,0:35:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我把这个暗示植入了你的思想，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I put that suggestion in your mind, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.50,0:35:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是说了句你很饿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I said simply that you were hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.04,0:35:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,效果好得可怕，怪不得亚当斯医生遗之不用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Remarkably effective for a device that Dr. Adams was going to abandon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.17,0:35:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得我们应该再试试 - 对，来点不寻常的暗示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I think we should try this again. - Yes. Pick something unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.01,0:35:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不寻常的暗示，我们俩都能领会的那种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An unusual suggestion. Something we can both be sure of.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.69,0:35:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在圣诞晚会上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At the Christmas party,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.23,0:35:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们相遇了，我们跳舞了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we met, we danced.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.07,0:36:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你说起了星星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You talked about the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.70,0:36:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在希望事情往另外一个方向发展\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I suggest now that it happened in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.83,0:36:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你一把抱起我，带我去了你的船舱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You swept me off my feet and carried me to your cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.75,0:36:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.59,0:36:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，要是被你的下属撞见，你带我来了这儿…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, if your crew saw you carry me here...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.18,0:36:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我的下属会发誓保守秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My crew is sworn to secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.43,0:36:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我的名声，我是说，我们还是初次见面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But my reputation. I mean, just having met like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.15,0:36:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，要是你真心喜欢我，那就另当别论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course, it would be different if you cared for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.86,0:36:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我编造一个谎言？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want me to manufacture a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.99,0:36:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,打包成圣诞礼物送给你？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wrap it up as a Christmas present for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.29,0:36:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.96,0:36:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我更希望你发自内心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I prefer honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.27,0:37:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，寇克舰长会来一次完全的真情流露\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now Captain Kirk is going to have a complete demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.82,0:37:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望他心里不要留存任何疑虑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want there to be no doubts whatsoever in his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.45,0:37:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯狂地爱上了海伦，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're madly in love with Helen, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.29,0:37:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你为了她，不惜撒谎，行骗，偷窃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'd lie, cheat, steal for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.13,0:37:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 宁愿牺牲你的事业，你的名声 - 不，医生，不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Sacrifice your career, your reputation. - No, doctor. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.59,0:37:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦啊，你感觉到了吗，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The pain. Do you feel it, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.43,0:37:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须得到她，不然痛苦会更加剧烈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must have her, or the pain grows worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.89,0:37:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,渴望得到她的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The pain, the longing for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.72,0:37:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,海伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.64,0:37:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经爱上她很多年了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For years you've loved her, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.35,0:37:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很多年 - 很多年了，我一直爱着你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- For years. - For years. I've loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.02,0:37:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须一直记好了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must continue to remember that, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.32,0:38:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在她走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.24,0:38:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,海伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.95,0:38:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,海伦，别走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helen, don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.66,0:38:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你，海伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need you, Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.37,0:38:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，舰长，你必须拿出你的相位武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, captain, you must take your phaser weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.21,0:38:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,把它扔在地上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and drop it on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.39,0:38:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，你要是不听话，痛苦就会加剧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, the pain increases unless you obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.31,0:38:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.77,0:38:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,…扔掉它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.57,0:38:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very good, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.82,0:38:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好，现在轮到通讯器了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very good, indeed. And now your communicator.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.99,0:38:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,把它扔在地上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Drop it on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.67,0:39:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克呼叫进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk to Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.93,0:39:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.47,0:39:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,…呼叫进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...to Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.92,0:39:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不，医生！不！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, Doctor! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.77,0:39:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经离开了治疗室，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They've taken you from the room, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.02,0:39:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在在自己的房间里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're in your own quarters now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.32,0:39:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,海伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.69,0:39:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,海伦，我已经爱上你很多年了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helen, for years I've loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.03,0:39:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,海伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.20,0:39:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 回想一下 - 我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Try to remember. - I've loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.87,0:39:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他把这些想法强行植入你的思想 - 很多年了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He placed all that in your mind. - For years.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.24,0:39:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,回想一下，亚当斯医生从我手中夺占了控制台\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Remember. Dr. Adams took the controls away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.83,0:39:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你回想起那种痛苦了吗？他的声音，想起来了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you remember the pain? And then his voice? Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.46,0:40:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.31,0:40:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我想起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.03,0:40:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,海伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.46,0:40:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.92,0:40:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,通风管道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The duct.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.81,0:40:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,帮忙拉一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Give me a hand here. Pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.94,0:41:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,空调系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Air conditioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.61,0:41:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这肯定连接到其他通风管道和隧道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It has to connect with other ducts and tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.65,0:41:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你爬进去找一找，它可能通向配电室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can get through this. It might lead to the power supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.66,0:41:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,短路的话，安全力场会被切断\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Short-circuited, it would cut off the security force field.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.83,0:41:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前培训过超高功率电路的知识吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you had any training in hyper-power circuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.16,0:41:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.00,0:41:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,兆伏级\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Megavoltage.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.04,0:41:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦失手碰错电线，你就没命了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Touch the wrong line, and you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.80,0:41:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,管它是什么，总不会比亚当斯的光线治疗室更糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anything's better than Adams' treatment room.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.93,0:41:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,又到治疗时间了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Time for another treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.19,0:41:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要反抗我，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please don't fight me, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.99,0:41:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你怀疑我的话，只会加剧痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The pain only gets worse when you doubt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.25,0:42:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你完全信任我 - 我信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You believe in me completely. - I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.34,0:42:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你完全信赖我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you trust me completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.34,0:42:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.93,0:42:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,…信赖你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.34,0:42:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,棒极了，舰长，我得表扬你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excellent, captain. I compliment you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.35,0:42:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗，上回凡·格尔德医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know Dr. Van Gelder was down on his hands and knees,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.23,0:42:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可是双手双膝跪地，痛得一塌糊涂呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}sobbing at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.85,0:42:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,太令我满意了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's so gratifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.69,0:42:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我可真幸运，实验的样本总是如此优异\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm so fortunate to have had a couple of excellent specimens to work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.82,0:42:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我从中学到了很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've learned a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.45,0:42:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女医生，她不见了，亚当斯医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The woman doctor. She's gone, Dr. Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.53,0:42:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻通知安全人员，莱西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Notify security at once, Lethe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.70,0:42:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她在哪儿，舰长？ - 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Where is she, captain? - I--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.67,0:42:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不知道 - 海伦去哪儿了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Don't know. - Where did you send her?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.09,0:42:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,给了她什么指令？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And with what instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.80,0:42:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.06,0:42:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.99,0:43:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,危险 勿碰
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.30,0:43:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 紧急通道D - 没用的，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Emergency channel D. - It's no good, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.64,0:43:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我无法突破他们的力场 - 再试试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I can't break through their force field. - Keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.21,0:44:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,主高压电源
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.19,0:44:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,把他放回椅子上，伊莱，找到那个女的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get him back in the chair, Eli. And find that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.89,0:45:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，力场消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, the force field is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.52,0:45:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我能直接把你送到故障源头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can send you right to the source of the interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.81,0:45:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,叫上一些安全人员，跟我一起走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get some security people and follow me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.81,0:45:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,传送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Energize.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.25,0:45:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,安全屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.17,0:46:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号，我是史波克，力场已经被关闭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise, this is Spock. Force field has been eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.85,0:46:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.58,0:46:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.54,0:46:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 海伦，你没事吧？ - 没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Helen, are you all right? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.84,0:46:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这样是不对的，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, this isn't right, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.63,0:46:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样是亚当斯医生干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Adams did this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.22,0:46:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当斯医生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Adams?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.10,0:46:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当斯医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.10,0:46:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,治疗室，跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The treatment room. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.90,0:47:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.37,0:47:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,电源开启了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The power came on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.88,0:47:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's dead, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.04,0:47:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,仪器的强度还不足以致命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The machine wasn't on high enough to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.30,0:47:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但他独自一人暴露在光线下面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But he was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.76,0:47:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,能想象心灵被那种东西掏空吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you imagine the mind emptied by that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.73,0:47:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至连一个折磨他的人都没有？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Without even a tormentor for company?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.23,0:47:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.92,0:48:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所有部门，正在检查安全状况，报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All sections. Security check in progress. Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.06,0:48:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，有一条来自坦塔罗斯殖民地的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, captain, there was a message from Tantalus Colony, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.32,0:48:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,凡·格尔德发来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was from Van Gelder.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.86,0:48:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他想告诉你光线治疗室被拆除了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He thought you'd like to know the treatment room had been dismantled,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.15,0:48:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,设备被摧毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the equipment destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.62,0:48:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.92,0:48:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很难相信人会因空虚而死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's hard to believe that a man could die of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.72,0:48:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你坐进那间屋子，就知道什么感受了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not when you've sat in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.73,0:49:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,带我们离开轨道，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take us out of orbit, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.03,0:49:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,1级曲速前进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ahead warp factor 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.07,0:49:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,收到，舰长，1级曲速前进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Acknowledged, captain. Warp factor 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.84,0:49:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,本集结束
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.93,0:49:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-=The Last Fantasy=-\N谢谢观赏
